Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Retrieves the value of a specific spawn arg.

Usage
-----

*string* getKey( *string* **key** )

Parameters
----------

-   [key] - The spawn argument to return the value of.

Examples
--------

     
    void double_monster_gravity (entity ent_mon_this){
    string mon_class;
     
        mon_class=ent_mon_this.getKey("className");
        //more code here
        sys.spawn(mon_class);
     
    }

Notes
-----

This script event returns the value of the specified spawn argument as a
string.

